mobilio , touran<br />\n矮身7人 ： wish , stream , 柯打屎 <br />\n7人suv : q7 , outlander</blockquote><br />\n仲有老闆級7人 ： alphard , elgrand<br />\n矮身有電門7人 ： mazda5 ,mazda8 ,presage"},{"pid":"704829b4ff1017ddb70aac405c009bd594f22da3","tid":84574,"uid":6160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舊odyssey<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加埋包圍硬避震<br />\n感覺自己似車手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">車屋企人時被屌到仆街</span></span></blockquote><br />\n我上一部都係odyssey<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上手改到好跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係執上一手<br />\n又係改到好跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n另外油錢都要考慮<br />\n我一個星期出車兩三日<br />\n全市區短程<br />\n好小心咁揸都做唔到8L/km<br />\n我一個月大約油錢$750（-2.3後）"},{"pid":"19a80fa0741e8996fceda567a048f4252930df81","tid":84574,"uid":30929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:13:41.000Z","msg":"Vellfire"},{"pid":"b998f27916eb0e89252013dc42cf58d639a66ca3","tid":84574,"uid":17929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:16:01.000Z","msg":"我上年年中買車前試咗幾部7人車<br />\n<br />\nstepwgn：得兩個氣袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔音差，薄皮，但靚仔，空間感夠大，尾門方便，有電門，1500cc 牌費平，turbo夠力！但30個，我覺得唔值<br />\n<br />\nOdyssey：隔音一流！夠力，空間感都夠，電門方便！有360鏡頭，自動泊車！齋版都要接近40個，full opt要40幾，我有d over筆直<br />\n<br />\nMazda8: 隔音僅次於odyssey，全皮椅，空間一流，三隻電門夠方便！力水都ok👍 價錢唔貴，27個左右就有<br />\n<br />\nKiaSorento：全皮，大天窗天幕，suv個樣靚仔，三排都要氣袋，三排都要冷氣風口，空間感絕對一流，第三排都闊落，前排冷暖電椅，自動泊車，鋼水夠，隔音同odyssey差唔多，full load都夠力，不過無電門，車身高，老人家上落可能唔方便，電油版就油錢貴，柴油版就平好多，full opt 36個<br />\n<br />\n最後，我揀咗Sorento，而家都無後悔到👍"},{"pid":"402fd648e25e143a90202243da6d9a81bd27ffa6","tid":84574,"uid":53510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:18:04.000Z","msg":"揸緊部大霸王，又型又舒服"},{"pid":"4e145fe05ca6a82d6a87364bdba796990e007362","tid":84574,"uid":15404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:18:51.000Z","msg":"日產serena <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n28萬算唔錯"},{"pid":"702023641708b1053793246fdff3569d1a175891","tid":84574,"uid":17929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上年年中買車前試咗幾部7人車<br />\n<br />\nstepwgn：得兩個氣袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔音差，薄皮，但靚仔，空間感夠大，尾門方便，有電門，1500cc 牌費平，turbo夠力！但30個，我覺得唔值<br />\n<br />\nOdyssey：隔音一流！夠力，空間感都夠，電門方便！有360鏡頭，自動泊車！齋版都要接近40個，full opt要40幾，我有d over筆直<br />\n<br />\nMazda8: 隔音僅次於odyssey，全皮椅，空間一流，三隻電門夠方便！力水都ok👍 價錢唔貴，27個左右就有<br />\n<br />\nKiaSorento：全皮，大天窗天幕，suv個樣靚仔，三排都要氣袋，三排都要冷氣風口，空間感絕對一流，第三排都闊落，前排冷暖電椅，自動泊車，鋼水夠，隔音同odyssey差唔多，full load都夠力，不過無電門，車身高，老人家上落可能唔方便，電油版就油錢貴，柴油版就平好多，full opt 36個<br />\n<br />\n最後，我揀咗Sorento，而家都無後悔到👍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n漏咗： Sorento都有自動泊車，前後sensor，keyless，188匹，2400cc"},{"pid":"bdd1d1e66188d648237cb3c54328a5e1536906b8","tid":84574,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"冇人講大霸王<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b115da54e147e1181b141a60649f7fa209cc649","tid":84574,"uid":17929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:21:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舊odyssey<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加埋包圍硬避震<br />\n感覺自己似車手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">車屋企人時被屌到仆街</span></span></blockquote><br />\n我上一部都係odyssey<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上手改到好跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係執上一手<br />\n又係改到好跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 